<plot>A scientist swims underwater at night, her body adorned with pulsing electric lights. A blind man sends giant soap bubbles floating across a lake, filled with his memories. Children play innocently on a raft, as they drift downstream towards the edge of a perilous waterfall. Night Vision is a story 'made-up' by a woman undergoing a psychological test. A story about people who can see in the face of darkness.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?396113</url></doc>
